  .container
    %br
    - if notice
      .alert
        = notice
    - if alert
      .alert
        = alert
    %h1{style: "font-family: 'Proxima Nova Semi'"} Giving you the power to CREATE A better community.
    %h2 Every community has great projects that can’t get off the ground. But with Uruut, yours can be different. Your park needs a new playground? Uruut it. Need a new library? Uruut it. Senior center? Bike path? Dog park? Uruut it. That’s why we’re here – to help you strengthen your community.
    .btn.brown
      = link_to "#{user_signed_in? ? 'javascript:void(0)' : new_user_registration_path}", class: "#{'error-sign-up' if user_signed_in?}" do
        Sign Up Now
        %span
    %h5
      = link_to "#partner", :class => 'learn-more' do
        Learn More
        %span
