%section.full-width.partner#partner
  .container
    .marketing.float-left
      %h3 A NEW KIND OF CROWDFUNDING PLATFORM.
      %h2 Unlike others, Uruut is the only platform specifically designed to make your individual contributions go further -much further - by also supporting business and foundation funding.
    .pie-chart.float-right
      = image_tag "pie-chart.png"

%section.full-width.better
  .container
    %h3 WHAT MAKES URUUT BETTER?
    %h2 A greater chance for funding success. Bottom line.
    %p By harnessing three different funding sources, projects have a much better chance of reaching their goal.
    .graphic-1
      = image_tag "suitcase.png"
      .content
        %h5 Business Sponsors
        %p Uruut offers businesses and CSR organizations an opportunity to align to high-impact community projects and programs.  This directly connects you to customers and the local community while increasing brand awareness and social responsibility reach.
        = link_to funding_sources_pages_path, :class => "btn" do
          learn more
          %span
    .graphic-2
      = image_tag "individual.png"
      .content
        %h5 Individual CONTRIBUTORS
        %p Uruut offers you the opportunity to support projects you value, keeping your generosity targeted and connecting you to the lives you touch. When you join with thousands of other caring donors, there’s no stopping what a crowd can do.
        = link_to funding_sources_pages_path, :class => "btn" do
          learn more
          %span
    .graphic-3
      = image_tag "family.png"
      .content
        %h5 Foundations
        %p For private, family and corporate foundations, Uruut offers a marketplace of vetted ideas, enabling foundations to easily screen, search and provide support to projects and causes relevant to your mission.
        = link_to funding_sources_pages_path, :class => "btn" do
          learn more
          %span

%section.full-width.transparency
  .container
    %h3 ACCOUNTABILITY & TRANSPARENCY
    %h2 Other crowdfunding platforms essentially say, “OK, the project is funded. Our job is done.”
    .float-left
      = image_tag "laptop.jpg"
    .marketing.float-left
      %p This is a foreign sentiment to us. While others disengage after a project has been funded, for Uruut, getting a project funded is just the beginning. We regard accountability and transparency as an absolute necessity, because you should know exactly how your resources are being applied, and that promises are being kept.  You should be connected to the lives your donations touch, so we’ve built a robust application that democratizes the funding process by providing insight into post-funding budget and project status.

%section.full-width.who-should-use
  .container
    %h3 WHO IS URUUT FOR?
    %h2 Anyone who wants to strengthen their community and raise their odds of fundraising success.
    %p While Uruut is open to many types of projects, we specialize in working with the following:
    .graphic-1
      = image_tag "municipalities.png"
      .content
        %h5 Municipalities
        %p Cities and local jurisdictions looking to form public/private partnerships that target underfunded or zero-funded projects and programs.

    .graphic-2
      = image_tag "member-organizations.png"
      .content
        %h5 Member Organizations
        %p Chambers of Commerce, local leadership organizations, PTAs, and others who need a helping hand with community-oriented initiatives.

    .graphic-3
      = image_tag "non-profits.png"
      .content
        %h5 CIVIC ORGANIZATIONS
        %p Community-focused civic organizations, schools, churches and other non-profits, looking to expand their reach and that seek greater transparency.

%section.full-width.make-it-happen
  .container
    %h2
      Connect. Cooperate.
      %span{:style => "color:#70bf4c;"} Take Action
    = link_to new_project_path, :class => "btn brown" do
      Get Funded
      %span

    = link_to browse_projects_path, :class => "btn" do
      Fund Projects
      %span


%section#error-sign.modal.hide.fade
  .modal-header{style: "height: 17px;"}
    %button.close{"aria-hidden" => "true", "data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"} ×
  .modal-body
    %p
      Thank you for your interest. I appears you are already signed on.
    %p
      If you reached this message in error please #{link_to "contact us", contact_pages_path}


:javascript
  if(window.opener) {
    window.opener.location.reload(true);
    window.close()
  }
  $(function() {
    $('.learn-more').click(function(e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      $('html, body').animate({
        scrollTop: $("#partner").offset().top
      }, 750);
    });

    $(".error-sign-up").click(function(){
      $("#error-sign").modal("show");

    })
  })
